Written by Ravi Kiran Kola

Star Rukshar Dhillon (Madhavi Pasupuleti).Ritika Nayak . Vishwak Sen (Arjun Kumar Allam). Vikram Veramaneni (Surya)

Production Dream Farmers. SVCC Digital. Sri Venkateswara Cine Chitra
